---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section id="complaints" class="complaints-section">
    <div class="complaints-container">
      <div class="complaints-header">
        <h1 class="section-title">Libro de Reclamaciones</h1>
        <p class="complaints-description">
          Tu opinión es importante para nosotros. Si tienes alguna queja o sugerencia, 
          por favor completa el siguiente formulario y nos pondremos en contacto contigo.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="complaints-content">
        <form class="complaints-form" action="#" method="POST">
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="nombre">Nombre *</label>
              <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" required placeholder="Ingresa tu nombre">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="apellido">Apellido *</label>
              <input type="text" id="apellido" name="apellido" required placeholder="Ingresa tu apellido">
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Correo Electrónico *</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="ejemplo@correo.com">
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="telefono">Teléfono (Opcional)</label>
            <input type="tel" id="telefono" name="telefono" placeholder="+51 999 999 999">
          </div>
          
        
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="problema">Describe tu problema o sugerencia *</label>
            <textarea id="problema" name="problema" rows="6" required placeholder="Describe detalladamente tu problema, sugerencia o consulta..."></textarea>
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Enviar Reclamación</button>
          </div>
          
          <div class="legal-notice">
            <p>Al enviar este formulario, aceptas que procesemos tus datos personales para dar respuesta a tu consulta. 
            Nos comprometemos a responder en un plazo máximo de 30 días hábiles.</p>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .complaints-section {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-bg) 0%, var(--color-bg-alt) 50%, var(--color-layer) 100%);
    padding: calc(90px + 4rem) var(--padding-x) 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .complaints-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    opacity: 0.1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .complaints-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .complaints-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    background: var(--grad-accent);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .complaints-description {
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .complaints-content {
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, rgba(58,36,26,0.4), rgba(42,26,19,0.6));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .complaints-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-group label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group select,
  .form-group textarea {
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(58,36,26,0.6), rgba(42,26,19,0.8));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.5;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .form-group input::placeholder,
  .form-group textarea::placeholder {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(58,36,26,0.8), rgba(42,26,19,0.9));
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(197,138,75,0.2), inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .form-group select {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .form-group textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 120px;
  }

  .submit-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(100deg, #8f5930, #c58a4b 65%, #d8b07d);
    color: #27160c;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.6px;
    border: none;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1rem;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 8px 20px -8px rgba(197,138,75,0.3);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, filter 0.3s ease;
    align-self: flex-start;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .submit-btn::after {
    content: '→';
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .submit-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    filter: brightness(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 12px 28px -10px rgba(197,138,75,0.4);
  }

  .submit-btn:active {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .submit-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent-soft);
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }

  .legal-notice {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .legal-notice p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .complaints-section {
      padding: calc(90px + 2rem) var(--padding-x) 2rem;
    }

    .complaints-content {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .complaints-form {
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .complaints-content {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
